      • importData

        void importData(Object objToImport,
              Map<Integer,Integer> projects,
              Map<Integer,Integer> subprojects)
                throws Exception
        Invoked if the selected the extension to import data.
        Parameters:
        objToImport - the deserialized import

        subprojects - the map contains a reference to the subproject id (old subproject id -> new subproject id)
